are actually calling me a demon.

79
00:05:11,880 --> 00:05:12,820
Ridiculous.

80
00:05:16,520 --> 00:05:19,120
Heavenly Lord Dacheng, don't be mad.

81
00:05:20,480 --> 00:05:22,640
How about I cook for you tonight
to make it up to you?

82
00:05:22,640 --> 00:05:23,640
What do you think?

83
00:05:26,920 --> 00:05:27,930
You can cook?

84
00:05:28,480 --> 00:05:29,920
I learned it from Madam Yang.

85
00:05:29,920 --> 00:05:31,380
What would you like to eat?

86
00:05:33,010 --> 00:05:34,010
