170
00:13:13,560 --> 00:13:15,040
I remember when you first got here,

171
00:13:15,040 --> 00:13:16,290
you didn't even reach my shoulder.

172
00:13:16,290 --> 00:13:18,350
Now your son is almost taller than me.

173
00:13:18,440 --> 00:13:21,110
Yes, Huaiyu's growing fast.

174
00:13:21,400 --> 00:13:23,130
He's grown much taller lately.

175
00:13:24,280 --> 00:13:25,340
That's wonderful.

176
00:13:26,010 --> 00:13:26,860
Take this.

177
00:13:36,080 --> 00:13:37,440
Sorry, My Lady,

178
00:13:38,020 --> 00:13:39,220
I cannot accept this.

179
00:13:40,280 --> 00:13:42,280
Huaiyu's a smart, hardworking boy.

180
00:13:42,320 --> 00:13:44,980
He shouldn't stay here
and waste his potential.

181
00:13:45,520 --> 00:13:48,160
Use the money to buy a house outside,

182
00:13:48,760 --> 00:13:50,820
and find him a proper school.

183
00:13:51,080 --> 00:13:53,010
With his potential,

184
00:13:53,520 --> 00:13:55,600
I believe he'll make something of himself.

185
00:13:55,600 --> 00:13:57,340
And you won't need
to worry about money anymore.

186
00:13:57,340 --> 00:13:59,140
Just enjoy the rest of your life.

187
00:14:03,760 --> 00:14:06,440
My Lady, I'm grateful for your offer,

188
00:14:06,760 --> 00:14:07,320
but…

189
00:14:08,520 --> 00:14:10,450
Since the day you saved me,

190
00:14:10,830 --> 00:14:12,360
my life has belonged to you.

191
00:14:13,250 --> 00:14:15,980
I swore before the statue
of God Hongmeng

192
00:14:17,600 --> 00:14:19,440
to serve you my whole life

193
00:14:19,800 --> 00:14:21,720
and be loyal to you until the end.

194
00:14:23,690 --> 00:14:26,540
I'm doing great.
I don't need looking after.

195
00:14:28,720 --> 00:14:30,650
I don't need your service anymore.

196
00:14:31,040 --> 00:14:32,770
There's no need for you to stay.

197
00:14:34,960 --> 00:14:35,440
My Lady.

198
00:14:36,760 --> 00:14:38,080
Please let me stay!

199
00:14:39,760 --> 00:14:40,420
My Lady!

200
00:16:22,070 --> 00:16:23,640
I'll be away for a while.

201
00:16:24,050 --> 00:16:25,640
If you truly wish to stay,

202
00:16:26,120 --> 00:16:28,320
then help me keep watch over Qichi Hall.

203
00:16:37,240 --> 00:16:38,320
Yes, My Lady.

204
00:16:39,640 --> 00:16:41,900
Then I'm leaving it to you, Steward Meng.

205
00:17:55,160 --> 00:17:58,150
[Qichi Hall]

206
00:18:03,600 --> 00:18:05,440
Master loves peace and quiet.

207
00:18:05,960 --> 00:18:08,290
Once your work is done,

208
00:18:08,680 --> 00:18:10,810
stay in your rooms and rest.

209
00:18:11,560 --> 00:18:12,760
Don't wander around.

210
00:18:13,440 --> 00:18:15,880
Especially, do not enter Master's room.

211
00:18:21,040 --> 00:18:26,320
Also, during winter,
Master loves sweet potatoes.

212
00:18:26,840 --> 00:18:30,830
Make sure to take good care of
the sweet potato field in the backyard.

213
00:18:31,440 --> 00:18:33,910
Water and fertilize it on time.

214
00:18:34,320 --> 00:18:36,250
Don't slack off, not even for a day.

215
00:18:36,710 --> 00:18:37,340
Yes.

216
00:18:38,710 --> 00:18:39,510
Steward Meng,

217
00:18:39,960 --> 00:18:42,320
I heard your grandson
is a government official.

218
00:18:42,320 --> 00:18:44,480
Why are you still here taking orders

219
00:18:44,480 --> 00:18:45,310
as a servant?

220
00:18:45,760 --> 00:18:46,400
Wouldn't it be better

221
00:18:46,400 --> 00:18:48,440
to leave this place
and enjoy a luxurious life

222
00:18:48,440 --> 00:18:49,440
with your family?

223
00:18:55,070 --> 00:18:57,480
Master doesn't like gossipy people.

224
00:18:57,510 --> 00:18:58,710
Neither do I.

225
00:18:59,720 --> 00:19:01,080
If you're staying here,

226
00:19:01,480 --> 00:19:04,110
speak less and work more.

227
00:19:04,800 --> 00:19:05,760
Understood.

228
00:19:07,080 --> 00:19:07,880
Steward Meng.

229
00:19:08,120 --> 00:19:09,580
A letter from your family.

230
00:19:11,960 --> 00:19:13,290
A letter from my family?

231
00:19:18,840 --> 00:19:21,070
It's from my grandson.

232
00:19:43,440 --> 00:19:46,910
[To my grandfather Meng Chi]

233
00:20:57,240 --> 00:20:58,020
My Lady.

234
00:21:00,480 --> 00:21:02,720
It's so late. What's the matter?

235
00:21:14,040 --> 00:21:15,840
I have a grandson—

236
00:21:16,920 --> 00:21:18,720
the one working as an official.

237
00:21:20,120 --> 00:21:22,920
I've just heard
he's been charged with something,

238
00:21:23,120 --> 00:21:26,080
and in a few days, he'll be executed.

239
00:21:27,360 --> 00:21:28,640
I know that boy.

240
00:21:29,560 --> 00:21:32,640
He's been pure and kind
since he was little.

241
00:21:33,360 --> 00:21:35,070
He'd never do anything bad.

242
00:21:36,000 --> 00:21:39,400
There has to be some mistake.

243
00:21:41,400 --> 00:21:42,120
My Lady.

244
00:21:43,560 --> 00:21:45,620
I know you're not an ordinary person.

245
00:21:46,960 --> 00:21:47,920
Please…

246
00:21:50,080 --> 00:21:51,080
help him.

247
00:21:54,120 --> 00:21:55,120
Help him, please.

248
00:22:07,480 --> 00:22:09,340
Everything happens for a reason.

249
00:22:10,040 --> 00:22:12,640
Even I cannot interfere with it.

250
00:22:30,360 --> 00:22:34,640
Forgive me
for disturbing you at this hour.

251
00:22:36,080 --> 00:22:36,880
It's alright.

252
00:22:37,560 --> 00:22:39,560
It's late. You should head back now.

253
00:22:42,480 --> 00:22:44,080
Good night, My Lady.

254
00:22:45,400 --> 00:22:46,760
I'll take my leave.

255
